-x-R0_F1
en
conf t
license boot module c2900 technology-package securityk9
yes
do wr
do reload

en
conf t
hostname R0_F1
username MAIN_ISP password pppno3L0l
int gig0/2/0
description Az R1_F1 eszköz felé, az F1 telephely felé. / Towards the R1_F1 device, to the site of F1.
ip address 80.90.125.49 255.255.255.252
no sh
exit
int se0/1/0
description A MAIN_ISP eszköz felé, az ISP területéhez és a Projectenis többi telephelyeihez. / Towards the MAIN_ISP device, to the sites of the inner ISP territory and Projectenis.
ip address 80.90.125.46 255.255.255.252
encapsulation ppp
ppp authentication chap
no sh
exit
int gig0/3/0
description Az R2_F1 eszköz felé, az F1 telephely felé. / Towards the R2_F1 device, to the site of F1.
ip address 80.90.125.53 255.255.255.252
no sh
exit
router ospf 1
router-id 198.198.198.198
network 80.90.125.48 0.0.0.3 area 0
network 80.90.125.52 0.0.0.3 area 0
network 80.90.125.44 0.0.0.3 area 0
exit
username ISPadmin password cortex999
enable password enpass55
ip domain-name ISP.com
crypto key generate rsa
1024

ip ssh version 2
ip ssh authentication-retries 2
ip ssh time-out 120
line vty 0 15
transport input ssh
login local
exit
banner motd %This device is only accesable by registered authorized personnel within work hours. Accessing the device unregurarly, or any tampering that damages the owners and the comapny, will result in legal action being taken.%
do write




