banner motd %This device is only accesable by registered authorized personnel within work hours. Accessing the device unregurarly, or any tampering that damages the owners and the comapny, will result in legal action being taken.%


bba-group pppoe global
virtual-template 1
exit
username MAIN_ISP password ispAuth1234
ip local pool PPP_POOL 80.90.125.58 80.90.125.58
aaa new-model
aaa authentication ppp default local
interface Virtual-Template1
ip unnumbered gig0/1
peer default ip address pool PPP_POOL
ppp authentication chap
exit
int gig0/1
pppoe enable
no sh
exit


